				<h3 id="post-3075"><a href="http://tradewithdave.com/?p=3075" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Who Wants To Be A Slum Dog Trillionaire?">Who Wants To Be A Slum Dog Trillionaire?</a></h3>
				<small>Thursday, October 28th, 2010</small>

				<div class="entry">
					<div style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;"><a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-via="tradewithdave" data-count="vertical" data-url="http://tradewithdave.com/?p=3075">Tweet</a></div>
<p><a href="http://www.google.com/imgres?imgurl=http://forladiesbyladies.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/wwtbamproposal.jpg&amp;imgrefurl=http://forladiesbyladies.com/index.php/2009/05/05/8-completely-unscripted-game-show-marriage-proposals/&amp;usg=__iU_zjH3oKP3gQ2jjUMED2lqmdtQ=&amp;h=842&amp;w=1000&amp;sz=192&amp;hl=en&amp;start=31&amp;zoom=1&amp;itbs=1&amp;tbnid=GeaFpAx76lt7YM:&amp;tbnh=125&amp;tbnw=149&amp;prev=/images%3Fq%3Dwho%2Bwants%2Bto%2Bbe%2Ba%2Bmillionaire%2Blogo%26start%3D18%26hl%3Den%26sa%3DN%26gbv%3D2%26ndsp%3D18%26tbs%3Disch:1"><img src="http://t1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:GeaFpAx76lt7YM:http://forladiesbyladies.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/wwtbamproposal.jpg" alt="" width="149" height="125" /></a></p>
<p>In what can only be described as a made-for-television prime time extravaganza, the Federal Reserve tells the primary dealers that he wants to use a lifeline&#8230;  &#8220;ask the audience how much QE2 we need.&#8221;  Here&#8217;s the story from Bloomberg: <a href="http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-28/fed-asks-dealers-to-estimate-size-impact-of-debt-purchases.html">http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-28/fed-asks-dealers-to-estimate-size-impact-of-debt-purchases.html</a></p>
